- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of network analysis in leveraging the power of the network toolkit. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses the representation of big data and the use of algorithms for building the network. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the representation of data in different forms and the use of visualization tools for interactive exploration.
